<BLOCK>
A clear spray containing 1.0% clotrimazole BP.
</BLOCK>


<BLOCK>
Canesten atomiser spray also contains isopropanol (30%), propylene glycol and polyethylene glycol 400.  The spray is produced by an atomiser and contains no propellant.
</BLOCK>


<BLOCK>
The atomiser spray comes in a bottle containing 40ml.
</BLOCK>


<BLOCK>
Canesten atomiser spray is one of a group of medicines called imidazoles which are used to treat fungal skin infections.
</BLOCK>

